{"_id":"0F2DvO4syuUGCmS2","name":"The Wild Swans Gang - Descriptor","type":"descriptor","img":"icons/svg/book.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"<p>We are a band of brothers and we specialize in fighting the \nOrder’s emissaries. Thanks to the curse that has been inflicted on us, we can \ntransform into swans.\n1 Wound (for each of the 11 gang members)</p>","notes":"bt-corebook-1-eng-final-screen-fixed [2022-07-01].pdf, page 51.","positive":"We are a band of brothers and we specialize in fighting the \nOrder’s emissaries. Thanks to the curse that has been inflicted on us, we can \ntransform into swans.\n1 Wound (for each of the 11 gang members)","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1781556805448,"modifiedTime":1781556805448,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"1cgd9Gledv5V2OvX","name":"White Rose and Red Rose - Descriptor","type":"descriptor","img":"icons/svg/book.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"<p>I hunt monsters and I have learned every bit \nof knowledge relevant to the fight against darkness. I am the \nmind that uncovers evil and my sister is the arm that punishes it.</p>","notes":"bt-ls-book-1-ENG-SCREEN.pdf, page 18.","positive":"I hunt monsters and I have learned every bit \nof knowledge relevant to the fight against darkness. I am the \nmind that uncovers evil and my sister is the arm that punishes it.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1781556805448,"modifiedTime":1781556805448,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"3z0StqjeaHezJ1yT","name":"The Little Oni - Descriptor","type":"descriptor","img":"icons/svg/book.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"<p>I am a six-year-old child and I easily get angry. \nI possess the strength and endurance of ten men. I become \nattached to the Hunters because I feel they are similar to me.</p>","notes":"bt-ls-book-1-ENG-SCREEN.pdf, page 16.","positive":"I am a six-year-old child and I easily get angry. \nI possess the strength and endurance of ten men. I become \nattached to the Hunters because I feel they are similar to me.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1781556805448,"modifiedTime":1781556805448,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"6kwpcsUh1nyWtGSw","name":"Brunhilde the Fighter - Descriptor","type":"descriptor","img":"icons/svg/book.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"<p>I am a seasoned commander, and my swordsmanship rivals even the most skilled warriors. I can tell the \nquality of a fighter at a glance.</p>","notes":"bt-ls-book-1-ENG-SCREEN.pdf, page 13.","positive":"I am a seasoned commander, and my swordsmanship rivals even the most skilled warriors. I can tell the \nquality of a fighter at a glance.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1781556805448,"modifiedTime":1781556805448,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"72s4V3VnNgwL8AWd","name":"The Roc - Descriptor","type":"descriptor","img":"icons/svg/book.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"<p>I am a huge egg, growing unnaturally large when \nsafely underground. My shell is hard as metal.</p>","notes":"bt-ls-book-1-ENG-SCREEN.pdf, page 14.","positive":"I am a huge egg, growing unnaturally large when \nsafely underground. My shell is hard as metal.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1781556805448,"modifiedTime":1781556805448,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"892oeuWeILRZUSXx","name":"Goldilocks and her War Bears - Descriptor","type":"descriptor","img":"icons/svg/book.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"<p>I am a young mercenary who combines fighting \nskills with uncontrolled fury. My loyal war bears are my family \nand no one can lay a finger on me.</p>","notes":"bt-corebook-1-eng-final-screen-fixed [2022-07-01].pdf, page 59.","positive":"I am a young mercenary who combines fighting \nskills with uncontrolled fury. My loyal war bears are my family \nand no one can lay a finger on me.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1781556805448,"modifiedTime":1781556805448,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"Bkhsys81l1ONZnTJ","name":"Poor Nello and The Faithful Patrasche - Descriptor","type":"descriptor","img":"icons/svg/book.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"<p>I am a poor boy who no longer has a home \nto live in. I dabble in painting and can turn my hand to all \nkinds of work.</p>","notes":"bt-ls-book-1-ENG-SCREEN.pdf, page 15.","positive":"I am a poor boy who no longer has a home \nto live in. I dabble in painting and can turn my hand to all \nkinds of work.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1781556805448,"modifiedTime":1781556805448,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"D6Q9292VE7xgQHsp","name":"The Ancient Enemy - Descriptor","type":"descriptor","img":"icons/svg/book.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"<p>I am an ancient and powerful creature. \nMy body was formed in the fires of creation and common \nweapons can do nothing against me.</p>","notes":"bt-corebook-1-eng-final-screen-fixed [2022-07-01].pdf, page 50.","positive":"I am an ancient and powerful creature. \nMy body was formed in the fires of creation and common \nweapons can do nothing against me.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1781556805448,"modifiedTime":1781556805448,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"E9AZlMTulO3aqGQJ","name":"The Silent - Descriptor","type":"descriptor","img":"icons/svg/book.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"<p>I am an unscrupulous killer, I hate humanity \nand the body to which I am condemned. My voice is reduced \nto a faint whisper, which weakened my Siren powers but did \nnot take them away.</p>","notes":"bt-corebook-1-eng-final-screen-fixed [2022-07-01].pdf, page 52.","positive":"I am an unscrupulous killer, I hate humanity \nand the body to which I am condemned. My voice is reduced \nto a faint whisper, which weakened my Siren powers but did \nnot take them away.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1781556805448,"modifiedTime":1781556805448,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"EeihSZYSbCVwACIY","name":"The Wise Fox - Descriptor","type":"descriptor","img":"icons/svg/book.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"<p>I am an immortal spirit \nincarnated in the body of a talking fox \nand I have always watched over human \naffairs.</p>","notes":"bt-corebook-1-eng-final-screen-fixed [2022-07-01].pdf, page 54.","positive":"I am an immortal spirit \nincarnated in the body of a talking fox \nand I have always watched over human \naffairs.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1781556805448,"modifiedTime":1781556805448,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"KSKnSjKo77sRTRUc","name":"Gemba Tanuki and Mayu Kitsune - Descriptor","type":"descriptor","img":"icons/svg/book.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"<p>I am a good-natured acrobat who enjoys music and poetry. \nThanks to my friendly nature, I can make everyone like me.</p>","notes":"bt-ls-book-1-ENG-SCREEN.pdf, page 10.","positive":"I am a good-natured acrobat who enjoys music and poetry. \nThanks to my friendly nature, I can make everyone like me.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1781556805448,"modifiedTime":1781556805448,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"KkBBq04n9ZyzFQCC","name":"The King’s Unlikely Tailor - Descriptor","type":"descriptor","img":"icons/svg/book.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"<p>I am an anemic young man with a body covered in scars, escorted \nand aided by my rich friend who considers me his most precious possession.\n1 Wound</p>","notes":"bt-corebook-1-eng-final-screen-fixed [2022-07-01].pdf, page 67.","positive":"I am an anemic young man with a body covered in scars, escorted \nand aided by my rich friend who considers me his most precious possession.\n1 Wound","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1781556805448,"modifiedTime":1781556805448,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"NujKJNCjMzY5gZP8","name":"The Returning Wolf - Descriptor","type":"descriptor","img":"icons/svg/book.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"<p>I am the Returning Wolf: I am bad, hungry, \nand now I am the hunter.</p>","notes":"bt-corebook-1-eng-final-screen-fixed [2022-07-01].pdf, page 65.","positive":"I am the Returning Wolf: I am bad, hungry, \nand now I am the hunter.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1781556805448,"modifiedTime":1781556805448,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"PFMdtrnZM3JmzKwS","name":"The Periwinkle Peer - Descriptor","type":"descriptor","img":"icons/svg/book.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"<p>I am the best \nat everything I do and I must \nwin every challenge. I do not \nexcel in science and academic \nknowledge, but no one must \ndiscover this weakness of mine. I prefer to show off my \nphysical prowess and skill.</p>","notes":"bt-corebook-1-eng-final-screen-fixed [2022-07-01].pdf, page 49.","positive":"I am the best \nat everything I do and I must \nwin every challenge. I do not \nexcel in science and academic \nknowledge, but no one must \ndiscover this weakness of mine. I prefer to show off my \nphysical prowess and skill.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1781556805448,"modifiedTime":1781556805448,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"QNXXgNULQmjyxyBH","name":"Hans the Handsome - Descriptor","type":"descriptor","img":"icons/svg/book.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"<p>I am adept at flushing out and dealing with \nbeasts of all kinds. I avoid any reflective surface, for I cannot \nbear the sight of my true self.</p>","notes":"bt-ls-book-1-ENG-SCREEN.pdf, page 11.","positive":"I am adept at flushing out and dealing with \nbeasts of all kinds. I avoid any reflective surface, for I cannot \nbear the sight of my true self.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1781556805448,"modifiedTime":1781556805448,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"bBy3MwUoZ99lN8S3","name":"The Feral Musicians of Bremen - Descriptor","type":"descriptor","img":"icons/svg/book.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"<p>I am a place full of violence and suffering, \nable to awaken the deepest fears in the souls of those who \napproach.\n64</p>","notes":"bt-corebook-1-eng-final-screen-fixed [2022-07-01].pdf, page 64.","positive":"I am a place full of violence and suffering, \nable to awaken the deepest fears in the souls of those who \napproach.\n64","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1781556805448,"modifiedTime":1781556805448,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"coHjbbWqSriiP5Qd","name":"Alfred Leaves the Talking Ghost - Descriptor","type":"descriptor","img":"icons/svg/book.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"<p>I am a usurer of secrets, and will sell them at \na high price. If I die, I become a ghost until I am reborn in \nflesh and blood.\n61\n1 Wound</p>","notes":"bt-corebook-1-eng-final-screen-fixed [2022-07-01].pdf, page 61.","positive":"I am a usurer of secrets, and will sell them at \na high price. If I die, I become a ghost until I am reborn in \nflesh and blood.\n61\n1 Wound","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1781556805448,"modifiedTime":1781556805448,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"gI62s4zQcC82nBgX","name":"Orcus the Guardian - Descriptor","type":"descriptor","img":"icons/svg/book.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"<p>I am a giant of incredible strength and repulsive \nappearance. I serve the Order as the Hunters’ Guardian and \nexecute every order to the best of my ability.</p>","notes":"bt-corebook-1-eng-final-screen-fixed [2022-07-01].pdf, page 58.","positive":"I am a giant of incredible strength and repulsive \nappearance. I serve the Order as the Hunters’ Guardian and \nexecute every order to the best of my ability.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1781556805448,"modifiedTime":1781556805448,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"hEHsLhmcFsGETQXO","name":"Frog Face - Descriptor","type":"descriptor","img":"icons/svg/book.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"<p>I am a wealthy, deformed noble, using my \nresources to achieve my purposes.</p>","notes":"bt-corebook-1-eng-final-screen-fixed [2022-07-01].pdf, page 46.","positive":"I am a wealthy, deformed noble, using my \nresources to achieve my purposes.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1781556805448,"modifiedTime":1781556805448,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"jvfCVi2Gz2mZLyhu","name":"Ambrose the Sorcerer known as Old Merlin - Descriptor","type":"descriptor","img":"icons/svg/book.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"<p>I am an ancient sorcerer, my body is weak, but my magical \npower is unmatched.\n1 Wound</p>","notes":"bt-corebook-1-eng-final-screen-fixed [2022-07-01].pdf, page 45.","positive":"I am an ancient sorcerer, my body is weak, but my magical \npower is unmatched.\n1 Wound","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1781556805448,"modifiedTime":1781556805448,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"ltNWBKRZVbnzIBjx","name":"Polonia “the Fairy” and Perez “the Rat” - Descriptor","type":"descriptor","img":"icons/svg/book.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"<p>I am a skilled doctor who can operate with extreme precision. \nWith my scalpels, I can extract a tooth with a single stroke.</p>","notes":"bt-ls-book-1-ENG-SCREEN.pdf, page 7.","positive":"I am a skilled doctor who can operate with extreme precision. \nWith my scalpels, I can extract a tooth with a single stroke.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1781556805448,"modifiedTime":1781556805448,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"pKkl8FY8EpScagyf","name":"Oakheart the Lady of the Woods - Descriptor","type":"descriptor","img":"icons/svg/book.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"<p>I am a twisted, lonely being \nwho wanders the forests and rewards \ncompanionship and kindness with \nboons.\n1 Wound</p>","notes":"bt-corebook-1-eng-final-screen-fixed [2022-07-01].pdf, page 63.","positive":"I am a twisted, lonely being \nwho wanders the forests and rewards \ncompanionship and kindness with \nboons.\n1 Wound","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1781556805448,"modifiedTime":1781556805448,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"pPHnjvg7Cp61gOza","name":"Sinbad the Traveler of a Thousand Seas - Descriptor","type":"descriptor","img":"icons/svg/book.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"<p>I am an experienced traveler and have seen \nevery known land. I get bored easily if I’m not interested in \nwhat I’m doing.\n1 Wound</p>","notes":"bt-corebook-1-eng-final-screen-fixed [2022-07-01].pdf, page 60.","positive":"I am an experienced traveler and have seen \nevery known land. I get bored easily if I’m not interested in \nwhat I’m doing.\n1 Wound","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1781556805448,"modifiedTime":1781556805448,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"pbMV5w0LDgQR3QyH","name":"The Masked Swashbuckler - Descriptor","type":"descriptor","img":"icons/svg/book.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"<p>I am a cunning cat who can pretend to be \nhuman thanks to a magical mask. I put myself at the service \nof the highest bidder without qualms and I use my countless \nlives to get the better of every problem.\n56</p>","notes":"bt-corebook-1-eng-final-screen-fixed [2022-07-01].pdf, page 56.","positive":"I am a cunning cat who can pretend to be \nhuman thanks to a magical mask. I put myself at the service \nof the highest bidder without qualms and I use my countless \nlives to get the better of every problem.\n56","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1781556805448,"modifiedTime":1781556805448,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"qsyutCeDWQr8Ezle","name":"Fire Eater the Puppeteer - Descriptor","type":"descriptor","img":"icons/svg/book.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"<p>I am a skilled alchemist and puppet master. \nHidden within my clothes are all kinds of tools and weapons, \neach useful for disassembling and reassembling bodies, whether \nof flesh or wood.</p>","notes":"bt-corebook-1-eng-final-screen-fixed [2022-07-01].pdf, page 55.","positive":"I am a skilled alchemist and puppet master. \nHidden within my clothes are all kinds of tools and weapons, \neach useful for disassembling and reassembling bodies, whether \nof flesh or wood.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1781556805448,"modifiedTime":1781556805448,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"vdV4FhWYai1Eajt8","name":"The Regiment of Giants - Descriptor","type":"descriptor","img":"icons/svg/book.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"<p>We are cowards and poorly trained soldiers, \nbut our reputation as fearsome Giants allows us to fool people.\n1 Wound (20 Company members)</p>","notes":"bt-ls-book-1-ENG-SCREEN.pdf, page 9.","positive":"We are cowards and poorly trained soldiers, \nbut our reputation as fearsome Giants allows us to fool people.\n1 Wound (20 Company members)","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1781556805448,"modifiedTime":1781556805448,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"x3IYvjNrsmo4Y6iF","name":"The Mothers of Fate - Descriptor","type":"descriptor","img":"icons/svg/book.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"<p>We are three sisters, we never show our real \nidentity, but we twist fate to our pleasure thanks to our \npowerful magic.</p>","notes":"bt-corebook-1-eng-final-screen-fixed [2022-07-01].pdf, page 68.","positive":"We are three sisters, we never show our real \nidentity, but we twist fate to our pleasure thanks to our \npowerful magic.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1781556805448,"modifiedTime":1781556805448,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"zu5V0IbGj227sK4t","name":"Harlequin the Servant - Descriptor","type":"descriptor","img":"icons/svg/book.svg","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{},"system":{"description":"<p>I am a skilled servant and can adapt to any task given to me. I \nalways find ways to carry out orders with as little effort as possible.</p>","notes":"bt-ls-book-1-ENG-SCREEN.pdf, page 6.","positive":"I am a skilled servant and can adapt to any task given to me. I \nalways find ways to carry out orders with as little effort as possible.","negative":"","exhausted":false,"xpMarked":false,"specialization":false,"sceneUsed":false},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.351","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.0","createdTime":1781556805448,"modifiedTime":1781556805448,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
